quotes.quote: To have more than you've got, become more than you are.
The more one does the more one can do.
Less is only more where more is no good.
We are more than the parts that form us.
Do more than dream. Work.
Be more than you seem to be.
To see more is to become more.
If you want to earn more, learn more.
Create more value than you capture.
There is more to life than surviving.
You are more powerful than you think.
To have more, you've got to become more.
More is learned in pain than in pleasure.
The more you look, the more you will see.
The more you know the less you understand.
The more a man knows, the more he forgives.
More always means worse.
Life is more valuable than money.
Listen more often than you speak.
Be more grateful, and less worried.
Trust yourself, you know more than you think you do.
Always give more than what's expected.
The more one judges, the less one loves.
Remember that the more you know, the less you fear.
The more you dream the more you achieve.
The more you think, the more time you have.
The more you care, the stronger you can be.
The more we learn, the more questions arise.
